üéÆ How to Play

1.Choose a Section: Click on a section card (e.g., Geography, Science, History) to start the quiz.

2.Answer Questions: Each section has a series of challenging and fun questions.
3.Earn Points: For every correct answer, your score increases.
4.Compete on the Leaderboard: Enter your name to save your score and compete with other players.



